public class UIExportRDFDialog
extends UIDialog
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, IUIConstants

UIExportRDFDialog defines the export dialog, that allows the user to export PC Map/List Views to an XML document formatted for RDF.

THIS CLASS IS NOT CURRENTLY USED.
